        Finds a solution by trying out all possible moves.
        Parameters:
        initial - the initial configuration of the robots
        maxMoves - the maximal number of moves to be searched
        Returns:
        a List of configurations representing the moves of the solution found, or null if none could be found withing maxMoves.
